Woodcutting chest
Type: Container

A beautiful ornate wooden chest, decorated with different kinds of tree bark. It was hidden between the roots of a tree you cut down.

Woodcutting chest is an openable treasury item. It can drop while doing Woodcutting activities, and can be obtained from some other sources. These Chests are the only way to obtain some Woodcutting based Equipment. They can have the odds of finding them increased with the Chest Finding equipment attribute.

Loot Tables

These are the sub-tables for the various materials, coins, and items that can come from these chests.

These treasury items take 4 independent loot rolls when they are opened.
